            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...I hope I'm getting better at this, now that I've been synthesizing other items besides just medicine..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "But if anyone asked me if I was doing alchemy or not, I still wouldn't know..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "It's like I'm self-taught...or even creating my own style. I haven't been too exact with the measurements, either."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "It's kinda scary, thinking that my style might be completely wrong."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "If there was someone I knew who was knowledgeable about synthesis, I could learn from them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I know, Mr. Keith! ...Probably won't teach me anything, so that's a no-go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "But still, I'm curious to hear stories from people who know how to do alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...oh! I should go ask Bell! She gave me that book...!"
